===Etymology===
From [[monetary]], from Latin [[monetarius]], from [[moneta#Latin|monēta]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{lb|en|economics}} The doctrine that [[economic]] systems are controlled by variations in the [[supply]] of [[money]].
# {{lb|en|economics}} The [[political]] doctrine that a nation's [[economy]] can be controlled by regulating the [[money supply]].

